&gt; I would suggest a test for anybody on this forum.  Set you ghost box at a super fast rate, then just sit back and listen.  After a while you will hear them talk, but you have to get used to listening that way.
&gt; 
&gt; I feel that it&#39;s the only legitimate way to do this.  Just my opinion on that topic.  If i hear someone&#39;s file with a slow sweep, i ignore it as communication for the most part.
